Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy ("Policy") describes how we ("us" or "our") collects, uses, shares and protects information about you when you use the "Pat" app ("App").

Information We Collect
We do not collect any personal information about you when you use the App. The app does not require any registration or login, and the data you input inside the app is only stored in your local device.

We collect anonymous usage data about the app, in order to improve the product experience for you. This data contains no personally identifiable information about you. Here’s what we collect:

- Anonymous usage statistics—stuff like what integrations you use, and the number of times you interact with the app.
- Your country and OS language.
- The version number of the app you’re using.
- Crash logs.
- The type of iPhone you have and the version of iOS you’re running.

Changes to our Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.

Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at appsbyburak@gmail.com.

Last Update: March 2024.
